falltergeist
============
falltergeist requires the original game files from Fallout 2 or
Fallout 1 in order to run.

You must put the master.dat and critter.dat files into the falltergeist
data directory, that is, ~/.local/share/falltergeist/ or
${TRUEPREFIX}/share/falltergeist (for global installs)
